These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, motorbike, helicopter, bus, roller, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Transport   | airplane | bus | roller | motorbike | helicopter | train | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, brazilian, french, american, thai, polish
1. the polish is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is on the left of the american##1
4. the american is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the french is on the right of the thai##1
6. the polish is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian | thai | french | pakistani | polish |

